location.Description: Location of the Analysis Services resource.

sku.Description: Represents the SKU name and Azure pricing tier for Analysis Services resource.

tags.Description: Key-value pairs of additional resource provisioning properties.

tier.Description: The name of the Azure pricing tier to which the SKU applies. Possible values include: 'Development', 'Basic', 'Standard'

capacity.Description: The number of instances in the read only query pool.

asAdministrators.Description: An array of administrator user identities

backupBlobContainerUri.Description: The container URI of backup blob.

managedMode.Description: The managed mode of the server (0 = not managed, 1 = managed).

serverMonitorMode.Description: The server monitor mode for AS server

state.Description: The current state of Analysis Services resource. The state is to indicate more states outside of resource provisioning. Possible values include: 'Deleting', 'Succeeded', 'Failed', 'Paused', 'Suspended', 'Provisioning', 'Updating', 'Suspending', 'Pausing', 'Resuming', 'Preparing', 'Scaling'

provisioningState.Description: The current deployment state of Analysis Services resource. The provisioningState is to indicate states for resource provisioning. Possible values include: 'Deleting', 'Succeeded', 'Failed', 'Paused', 'Suspended', 'Provisioning', 'Updating', 'Suspending', 'Pausing', 'Resuming', 'Preparing', 'Scaling'

serverFullName.Description: The full name of the Analysis Services resource.

members.Description: An array of administrator user identities.
